<p>This delightful Calming Massage CD was specifically designed by Dr. Tim H. Tanaka to help calm the mind and regulate breathing.  This album is the perfect complement to a massage or any relaxation activity such as Yoga or Pilates.  The title of some of these melodic tracks include The Calming, Spheres of Serenity and Drifitng with the Clouds, giving you some indication as to the total relaxation theme of this CD.  Total play time is 61 minutes and features 12 tracks.</p>